        <item>
            <title>【教学】iOS 18.1 如何用 Apple Intelligence   只需 2 个设定 + 香港免 VPN 也可用</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/29/apple-ios18-1-apple-intelligence-in-hong-kong/software/ios-app/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-ios18-1-apple-intelligence-in-hong-kong</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/29/apple-ios18-1-apple-intelligence-in-hong-kong/software/ios-app/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 10:30:51 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[实用技巧]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple iOS 18.1]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS 18.1]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1271945</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 稍早前已正式推出 iOS 18.1，此次是 iOS 18 最大型的更新，即使不是身处美国的 iPhone 15 Pro、iPhone 16 用户也可以使用 Apple Intelligence 了。除了 Apple Intelligence，是次更新亦加强了相机控制功能，并加入了空间照片功能和通话录音功能。想知道你手上的电话是否支援 Apple Intelligence，可以参考我们先前的报道（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/25/ios-18-1/mobile-phone/">报道连结</a>）。</p><p>如果手上的 iPhone 是 iPhone 15 Pro 系列或最新的 iPhone 16，而且你的 AppleID 地区设定是香港、台湾，那么无须将 Apple ID 改为美国，直接使用现有 Apple ID，更改 iPhone 的语言和地区即可使用 Apple Intelligence。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271952" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_e1253-285x580.jpg" alt="" width="285" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_e1253-285x580.jpg 285w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_e1253.jpg 442w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 285px" /></p><h2 class="wp-block-heading">Step 1 开启设定更改语言为 English (US)</h2><p>升级至 iOS 18.1 后，需要开启「设定」，选择「一般」，点击「语言与地区」，将语言改为英文（美国）﹝English(US)﹞方可使用 Apple Intelligence。要注意一定要是 English (US)，设定了其他地区的 English 暂时未有 Apple Intelligence。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271970" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_0342-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_0342-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_0342-1.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 开启「设定」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271969" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/apple_ios181_1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/apple_ios181_1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/apple_ios181_1.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 进入「一般」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271971" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/apple_ios181_2-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/apple_ios181_2-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/apple_ios181_2.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 选择「语言与地区」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271972" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/apple_ios181_3-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/apple_ios181_3-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/apple_ios181_3.png 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 将语言设定为「English(US)」</p><h2 class="wp-block-heading">Step 2 开启 Apple Intelligence &amp; Siri</h2><p>将语言改为 English (US) 后，你就可以看见 Setting （设定）新增了 Apple Intelligence &amp; Siri。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271977" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/apple_ios181_4-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/apple_ios181_4-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/apple_ios181_4.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 现在就有 Apple Intelligence</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271977" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/apple_ios181_4-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/apple_ios181_4-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/apple_ios181_4.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 现在就有 Apple Intelligence</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271980" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/apple_ios181_5-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/apple_ios181_5-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/apple_ios181_5.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 点击「Turn On Apple Intelligence」</p><p>稍等一会，就可以使用最新的 Apple Intelligence 了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271981" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/photo_61254547327817-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/photo_61254547327817-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/photo_61254547327817.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 点击「Continue」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271983" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/photo_61254547327817-2-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/photo_61254547327817-2-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/photo_61254547327817-2.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 点击「Choose Notification to Summarize」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271984" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/photo_61254547327817-3-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/photo_61254547327817-3-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/photo_61254547327817-3.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 剔选你需要 AI 总结的通知</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271985" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/apple_ios181_6-694x376.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="376" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/apple_ios181_6-694x376.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/apple_ios181_6.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 上图为 Apple iOS 18.1 新增的功能</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/02/apple-ai-clean-up-ios-18-1-beta-3/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】iOS 18.1 AI 一键清相片路人杂物　旅游景点不再人头涌涌</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/28/ios-18-1-release/software/ios-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iOS 18.1 脱离测试版正式推出　可用机种 + 新功能介绍</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/25/ios-18-1/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iOS 18.1 懒人包　18 个必用新功能</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/29/apple-ios18-1-apple-intelligence-in-hong-kong/software/ios-app/">【教学】iOS 18.1 如何用 Apple Intelligence   只需 2 个设定 + 香港免 VPN 也可用</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
