            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1271927</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">香港金融管理局（金管局）与投资推广署合办香港金融科技周 2024（FinTech Week），今届规模是历届之冠，但想不到连场内食物的价钱，亦异常地贵，成为了全场焦点，引来网民笑指会方用了 AI 或高科技的方法煮牛肉面。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1271988 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/464807106_1115103543-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/464807106_1115103543-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/464807106_1115103543.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲场内食物的价钱异常地贵，早餐沙嗲牛肉面配菠萝油盛惠 125 元（图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/zDsj2FmPTXmv6Kmv/">Joey in Hong Kong Facebook</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1271989 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/464753789_9539927701-433x580.jpg" alt="" width="433" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/464753789_9539927701-433x580.jpg 433w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/464753789_9539927701.jpg 672w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 433px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲午餐价钱由最便宜 125 元至最贵 190 元（图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/zDsj2FmPTXmv6Kmv/">Joey in Hong Kong Facebook</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">金融科技周 2024 食物价格高昂引起不少网民的质疑，沙嗲牛肉面配菠萝油盛惠 125 元，当中沙嗲牛肉面更是强调以「大光面」作面底。有网民指价钱与实际品质不成正比，特别是「大光面」的普通食材竟成为卖点。有网民认为这类餐点通常平价，质疑为何标榜成贵价食材。对于标价 125 元的沙嗲牛肉面，网民以「CHEAP 野」形容，认为主办方过度抬高平价食材的价值。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1271928 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241028_-694x274.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="274" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241028_-694x274.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241028_.jpg 946w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲网民以「CHEAP 野」形容大光面（图片来源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3811539/page/3">LIHKG</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">亦有意见反讽，食物是卖给「富贵人家」或「金融才俊」的，即设定较高价位，目标是吸引较高收入的人士。有网民以「飞士价」形容昂贵的餐点，并表示场内提供的食物价格是针对有钱人，而非普通市民。更有网民笑指，会方运用了 AI 及高科技方法烹调牛肉面，所以才会卖得如此昂贵。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1271929 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241028_-1-600x580.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241028_-1-600x580.jpg 600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241028_-1.jpg 708w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 600px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有网民以「飞士价」形容昂贵的餐点，并表示场内提供的食物价格是针对有钱人（图片来源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3811539/page/3">LIHKG</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1271930 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241028_-2-613x580.jpg" alt="" width="613" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241028_-2-613x580.jpg 613w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241028_-2.jpg 660w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 613px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲更有网民笑指，会方运用了 AI 及高科技方法烹调牛肉面（图片来源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3811539/page/3">LIHKG</a>）</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3811539/page/3">LIHKG</a>、<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/zDsj2FmPTXmv6Kmv/">Joey in Hong Kong Facebook</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/29/fintech-week/fun-tech/">金融科技周 2024 沙嗲牛面卖 $125 成焦点，网民：AI 煮牛肉面？用科技煮面？</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
